title: DBZ Cooler's Revenge Soundtrack
description:
The soundtrack from the DBZ (Dragonball Z) movie "Cooler's Revenge" 

List of songs:

1. Reminded - Drowning Pool
2. Poison - Dust for Life
3. Seven Years - American Pearl
4. Under - Breaking Point 
5. Stay and Drown - Finger Eleven
6. Falling Down - Breaking Point
7. Mute - Drowning Pool
8. Told You So - Drowning Pool
9. Revelation - American Pearl
10.Phoenix - Breaking Point
11.The Game - Disturbed
12.Change(In the House of Flies) - Deftones

P.S. I only did this because the only place where I could find the soundtrack was Spotify, and not many people (including me) have Spotify Premium to listen to it offline. And there isn't even an official one that was made by DBZ, so I just found the songs and put them together for whoever wants to listen. Just remember to SEED
